title: 23 The Inner Battle
description:
This episode was not in our schedule. We stumbled upon the cottage you'll see behind me in the video. It prompted me to recall an "inner war" that changed my life years ago, beneath a red-tile roof just like this one.

New episodes every Monday. SUBSCRIBE wherever you get your podcasts.
